OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Roy Hayward
OL,5,FRoy Hayward, Age 98, Sherwood Rangers
OL,6,FYeomanry
OL,8,FInterviewed 22 November 2023
OL,10,FLanding after dark on the evening of D-
OL,11,FDay on Gold Beach as a reserve tank
OL,12,Fcrewman, Roy Hayward from the Isle of
OL,13,FWight was in an ammunition lorry
OL,14,Ffollowing a line of tanks as it moved
OL,15,Fforwards.
OL,17,FHe said: "We left from Southampton on
OL,18,F6 June.
OL,20,F"We landed in the dark that evening,
OL,21,Fand I was on Gold.
