OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Roy Hayward
OL,5,F"We moved down the lane and suddenly
OL,6,Fthere was a very large thud at the
OL,7,Ffront of our tank and we tried to
OL,8,Freverse and get out of trouble.
OL,10,F"But another shell arrived and this
OL,11,Ftime it penetrated and landed round
OL,12,Fand about my feet and there was an
OL,13,Fexplosion.
OL,15,F"It became absolutely essential that
OL,16,Feverybody got out of the tank.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
