OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Roy Hayward
OL,5,F"The crew all left alright but the
OL,6,Fsergeant obviously didn't know what
OL,7,Fwas happening and before I could get
OL,8,Fout I had to get him out of the
OL,9,Fcockpit and I then managed to crawl
OL,10,Faway from the tank which was beginning
OL,11,Fto get a bit hot.
OL,13,F"In the time I was getting out I had
OL,14,Freceived burns to my right hand and I
OL,15,Fsaw my right leg was completely
OL,16,Fsmashed below the knee and I had lost
OL,17,Fthe front of my left foot.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
